title: Peer Pressure Will Help You Dominate or Do Nothing, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO4
description: Peer pressure can make you or break you.  Your peer group largely determines your success in both business and life.  So it is critical to choose your friends wisely.  Do they influence you to dominate--or do nothing?
